data.description: Here is your chance to not only live in Morristown, but to live in an adorable home. To top it  all off, the owner has made several upgrades to the home and is ready for you to move right in. There is a new Vapor Barrier in the crawl space along with a $1,000 dehumidifier added too. All appliances stay and a great outdoor shed in the backyard for  storage. New water heater installed March 2021,new tub surround and so many more upgrades. Spacious floorplan, big eat in kitchen and two good size bedrooms. Come check out this home because this is a cutie!
